- if @hub
  %h2.title #{@hub['Name']} Map Preview
  %p
    Here you can see a preview of how your hub looks (or will soon look) on the
    map! The
    %a{href: 'https://sunrisemovement.org/hubs'} actual hub map
    might be up to 15 minutes out of date, and there might be minor spacing or
    font differences.
  %br
  .wrapper1{style: 'max-width: 1600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 120px;'}
    .wrapper2{style: 'width: 74.995%; max-width: calc(100% - 1em); margin: 0 auto;'}
      %iframe{style: 'width: 100%; height: 434px', srcdoc: File.read('public/hub_map.html').gsub("https://sunrise-hub-json.s3.amazonaws.com/hubs.json", "/my_hub_json")}

- else
  %h2.title Full Hub Map Preview
  .wrapper1{style: 'max-width: 1600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 120px;'}
    .wrapper2{style: 'width: 74.995%; max-width: calc(100% - 1em); margin: 0 auto;'}
      %iframe{style: 'width: 100%; height: 434px', src: 'hub_map.html'}
